## Appendix: Comparable Success Stories

### Penn Avenue Cultural District (Pittsburgh)
- Transformed from declining corridor to thriving arts district
- $300M+ in public and private investment
- Model for cultural-led revitalization

### Walnut Street (Philadelphia)
- Complete street redesign with widened sidewalks
- 15% increase in retail sales
- Became city's premier shopping destination

### Pearl Street Mall (Boulder, CO)
- Pedestrian-only corridor with local businesses
- Generates $300M annually in economic activity
- Top tourist destination

### Church Street Marketplace (Burlington, VT)
- Revitalized downtown through pedestrian focus
- 2.5 million annual visitors
- 95% occupancy rate

